        &version.trunk.changelog;
        
         Implements ArrayAccess.
         Previously, the same array-style access of attributes and elements
         was possible without SimpleXMLElement
         explicitly implementing the
         ArrayAccess interface.
        
       
      
     
    
   
  

 
 
